answers.answer: Something is going on with your kidneys, UTI or preeclampsia are the most common. Both can be taken care of. I had UTIs and preeclampsia all through my first pregnancy and because I didn't stay on bed rest my kidneys began to fail and.put my baby in distress, it was a life or death situation for us both. My suggestion is you follow any and everything your Dr tells you to do.

question: A positive protein test in pregnancy means what?
title: protein in pregnancy
